    <item>
      <title>加拿大人口增长会减慢临时居民镇压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/canada-population-growth-slows-on-temporary-resident-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于移民的下降，加拿大在三年内以最慢的速度增加了新的居民，这使大流行的人口繁荣繁重，使经济紧张，对新移民造成了公众的情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/canada-population-growth-slows-on-temporary-resident-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 13:06:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟旨在加快资本市场监督计划的时间表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/eu-aims-to-speed-timeline-for-capital-markets-supervision-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲联盟承诺加快对资本市场更统一监督的提议的时间表，因为它试图推进一个对向国防等部门提供财务越来越重要的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/eu-aims-to-speed-timeline-for-capital-markets-supervision-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 13:03:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于欧洲央行政策的费用，法国银行损失扩大了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/bank-of-france-losses-widen-because-of-costs-from-ecb-policies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国银行报告说，在预订一次性收益后，2024年的损失扩大，并且随着近年来欧洲中央银行货币政策的迅速变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/bank-of-france-losses-widen-because-of-costs-from-ecb-policies</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚失败的最终IMF计划审查因缺少关键目标而失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/kenya-failed-final-imf-program-review-by-missing-key-targets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们称，肯尼亚未能在国际货币基金计划下的最终审查中获得关键的基准，从而减少了约8.5亿美元的支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/kenya-failed-final-imf-program-review-by-missing-key-targets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 12:56:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Guindos说，欧洲央行的利率途径尚未确定。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/ecb-s-path-for-interest-rates-isn-t-predetermined-guindos-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统路易斯·德·古诺斯（Luis de Guindos）表示，全球不确定性意味着欧洲中央银行无法在借贷成本将去向何处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/ecb-s-path-for-interest-rates-isn-t-predetermined-guindos-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 12:40:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
